  "bib_entries": {
    "17200359": {
      "title": "On the goodness-of-fit tests for some continuous time processes",
      "abstract": "We present a review of several results concerning the construction of the Cramer-von Mises and Kolmogorov-Smirnov type goodness-of-fit tests for continuous time processes. As the models we take a stochastic differential equation with small noise, ergodic diffusion process, Poisson process and self-exciting point processes. For every model we propose the tests which provide the asymptotic size $\\alpha $ and discuss the behaviour of the power function under local alternatives. The results of numerical simulations of the tests are presented."
